{"word":"κατεικάζω","slug":"κατεικάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατεικάζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to liken</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, aor1 <el>κατ-εικάσθην</el>, <i>to be</i> or <i>become like</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to guess, surmise</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <i>to suspect</i> evil, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}